'''約翰路易斯'''（'''John Lewis & Partners'''，原'''John Lewis'''）是一家英國高檔連鎖[[百貨商店|百貨商店]]，母公司是[[約翰路易斯合夥公司|約翰路易斯合夥公司]]，第一家約翰·路易斯於1864年開設於英國倫敦[[牛津街|牛津街]]。現於英格蘭、蘇格蘭和威爾士有43家商店，其中以位於倫敦者為最大。

2008年1月1日，牛津街的約翰路易斯得到英國女王[[伊莉莎白二世|伊莉莎白二世]]的[[皇家認證|皇家認證]]，成為[[英國皇室|英國皇室]]的家具雜貨用品的提供商，此前一年[[雷丁|雷丁]]的約翰路易斯也收到了類似的皇家認證<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.johnlewispartnership.co.uk/Display.aspx?MasterId=56b99c22-cfd9-4da9-a84c-badc3ee9c8d2&NavigationId=1329 |title=John Lewis awarded Royal Warrant |publisher=Johnlewispartnership.co.uk |date= |accessdate=20 April 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314042719/http://www.johnlewispartnership.co.uk/Display.aspx?MasterId=56b99c22-cfd9-4da9-a84c-badc3ee9c8d2&NavigationId=1329 |archivedate=2012年3月14日 }}</ref>。

2018年9月4日更名为“John Lewis & Partners”。<ref name="rebrand">{{cite web|title=John Lewis/Waitrose '& Partners' rebrand splits opinion|url=https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/john-lewis-waitrose-partners-rebrand-splits-opinion/1487632|website=Campaign Live|publisher=Haymarket Media Group|accessdate=16 July 2018|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129010707/https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/john-lewis-waitrose-partners-rebrand-splits-opinion/1487632|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==圣诞节广告==

自2007年开始约翰路易斯每年圣诞节都会发布一则特殊的圣诞节广告，因题材新颖而广受媒体报道<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bold|first1=Ben|title=John Lewis Christmas ads 2007 to 2015: from humble roots to national event|url=http://www.marketingmagazine.co.uk/article/1320008/john-lewis-christmas-ads-2007-2015-humble-roots-national-event|accessdate=8 November 2015|publisher=Marketing Magazine|date=6 November 2015|archive-date=2016-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426123136/http://www.marketingmagazine.co.uk/article/1320008/john-lewis-christmas-ads-2007-2015-humble-roots-national-event|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Regev">{{cite news|last1=Regev|first1=Dana|title=The Christmas commercials that turned into a smash hit|url=http://www.dw.com/en/the-christmas-commercials-that-turned-into-a-smash-hit/a-18835081|accessdate=8 November 2015|publisher=Deutsche Welle|date=8 November 2015|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130185021/https://www.dw.com/en/the-christmas-commercials-that-turned-into-a-smash-hit/a-18835081|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成为英国圣诞节文化的一部分<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/retailandconsumer/11212935/Its-funny-how-John-Lewis-Christmas-Advert-is-now-part-of-our-Christmas-countdown.html|newspaper=The Telegraph|title=It's funny how John Lewis Christmas Advert is now part of our Christmas countdown|last=Wallop|first=Harry|date=6 November 2014|accessdate=8 November 2015|archive-date=2017-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420083648/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/retailandconsumer/11212935/Its-funny-how-John-Lewis-Christmas-Advert-is-now-part-of-our-Christmas-countdown.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

